quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  18,32,Auze za fanizo la anthu awiri. Mmodzi wa iwo adali ndi minda iwiri ya mphesa imene tidazunguliza m’mbali mwake ndi mitengo ya tende ndipo tidaika pakati pake mbewu zina
  18,33,"Munda uliwonse umapereka zipatso zake, ndipo siupunguza chilichonse ndipo Ife tidatumphutsa mitsinje m’kati mwa mindayo"
  18,34,"Ndipo Iye adali ndi zipatso zambiri ndipo adanena kwa mnzake pamene anali kutsutsana naye nati, “Ine ndili ndi chuma chambiri kuposa iwe ndiponso ndili ndi anthu a ntchito amphamvu kwambiri.”"
  18,35,"Ndipo iye adalowa m’munda mwake modzitukumula yekha nati, “Ine sindiganiza kuti izi zidzatha ayi.”"
  18,36,"“Ndipo ine sindikhulupirira kuti ola la chionongeko lidzadza. Ndipo ngakhale nditabwezedwa kwa Ambuye wanga, ine ndikapeza malo abwino oposa awa.”"
  18,37,"Mnzake uja adati kwa iye, “Kodi iwe wam’kana Iye amene adakulenga iwe kuchokera ku dothi ndi kuchokera ku dontho la umuna ndipo adakuumba kukhala munthu?”"
  18,38,"Akakhala ine, Mulungu ndiye Ambuye wanga. Ine sindidzamufanizira Iye ndi china chilichonse"
  18,39,"Bwanji pamene iwe umalowa m’munda mwako, siudanene kuti, “Izi ndi zimene Mulungu wafuna ndipo kulibe mphamvu kwina kulikonse kupatula kwa Mulungu? Ngakhale iwe ukundiona ine kuti ndine wochepekedwa kwambiri m’chuma ndi ana.”"
  18,40,“Mwina Ambuye wanga akhoza kundipatsa munda wabwino oposa wako ndi kutumiza ziphaliwali kuchokera kumwamba ndi kusandutsa nthaka kukhala yosabereka.”
  18,41,“Kapena kuzamitsa madzi ake kuti iwe usawapeze.”
  18,42,"Ndipo zipatso zake zidaonongeka. Ndipo iye adayamba kufikisa zikhato zake mwachisoni chifukwa cha zonse zimene adaononga pa mindayi chifukwa zonse zidaonongeka. Ndipo iye adati: “Kalanga ine! Ndikanadziwa, sindikanaphatikiza milungu ina ndi Ambuye wanga!”"
  18,43,Ndipo iye adalibe gulu lomuthandiza polimbana ndi Mulungu ndiponso adalibe mphamvu zoti adzitetezere kapena kudzipulumutsira
  18,44,"Kumeneko chitetezo chidzakhala chochokera kwa Mulungu, Mwini choonadi. Iye ndiye ali ndi malipiro ndiponso mapeto abwino"